{"tid":1443752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[極緊急求推上熱門] 狗隻戰術已進化 我地要即時應對番","createTime":"2019-08-11T10:02:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:32:55.000Z","uid":138554,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"25c86fe3366cff5697d39d60947b9892785ad405","tid":1443752,"uid":138554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:02:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩又有兄弟俾狗用番差唔多戰術拉左<br />\n<br />\n狗二哥番左黎之後 狗既部署完全唔同哂<br />\n<br />\n呢個係重po 琴日係尖沙咀發夢 班狗縮哂番狗竇 但係keep住半個鐘左右射一兩粒TG落黎 佢既目的就係唔想我地班兄弟走 <span style=\"color: red;\">想我地留哂係原地</span> 同時狗竇入面班狗涼住冷氣on call 一等到旺角狗車增援一到就係<span style=\"color: red;\">幾邊包抄</span> 所以係11點幾嘆夠冷氣既狗同增援一齊夾番柏麗大道既兄弟 最後拉人 試問係街度又熱又冇武器既兄弟點會夠班養精蓄銳左咁耐既狗打 所以我提出幾點自己小小既建議：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.增設更多哨站</span><br />\n令所有兄弟了解番附近既情況 琴日就係衰在我地知得太遲搞到差d走唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.唔好做無意義既事</span><br />\n狗已經進化 我地仲好似以前咁留哂係原地既結果只有送頭 係狗竇前面停留根本唔會令佢放人/讓步<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3.加設更多路障</span><br />\n琴晚11點幾班狗包抄既時候基本上無咩路障去放慢佢地腳步 甚至有d係見到狗黎緊先整<br />\n<br />\n希望大家真係可以be water唔好戀戰<br />\n最後都要講番聲 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c8f97c83afc4756f171b1cb9647c726d1fbfe2","tid":1443752,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"721！"},{"pid":"910c9157eb4043eaf2e8005bcbdd5baa5c3b18ef","tid":1443752,"uid":296952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LxFQoQ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLxFQoQ5.jpg&h=30833ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1noRSKq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1noRSKq.png&h=fee569e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVAQoQ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVAQoQ6.jpg&h=9f20a70e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cQB4thM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcQB4thM.jpg&h=9f74304d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7vzUQv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7vzUQv6.jpg&h=d0edecd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48a71240d7874e5ccc81ed9be77f56b88597398c","tid":1443752,"uid":138554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"721!!!!"},{"pid":"993545bece6f6d779be5e5b1db33fe3bee504a76","tid":1443752,"uid":54921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:08:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>警察用緊閃擊戰</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n閃電戰（英語：Lightning War，德語：关于这个音频文件 Blitzkrieg 說明&middot;資訊）又稱閃擊戰，是一種軍事學說，採用移動力量迅速地出其不意地進攻，以避免敵人組織起防禦線。它脫胎於19世紀普魯士參謀部的戰術「開火滲透」（Fire and Infiltration）。<br />\n<br />\n德意志國防軍在二戰中大規模運用此戰術，對波蘭、法國和蘇聯的入侵非常有效，但在此之後失去優勢，因為閃電戰需要後方快速補給，必須開發特別的補給車輛、新的通信方法和分散化的指揮方式，戰線拉長後德國反而因為擴張過度陷入難以管理的困境。所謂「閃電戰」這個名詞並非出自德國人之口，而是德軍在法國戰役結束後，美國的時代雜誌率先提出的新名詞。"},{"pid":"ddc305727826fad299fb7992ae2d5f13902aa057","tid":1443752,"uid":71589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"推啊，手足be water"},{"pid":"c8effecaec73f9470ff20d712158426ca1dbe2b8","tid":1443752,"uid":111253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:12:41.000Z","msg":"打狗"},{"pid":"b701eb300b3a9a9423372d39f77c4016cb94b9fb","tid":1443752,"uid":138554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:17:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5559a1e9333a789f37232c4216a99a638bbbefcf","tid":1443752,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"好想大家打完一輪遠攻就即走，補彈再另一邊遠攻"},{"pid":"1a7b6dee9b2da27a6bb4608d12f075c2ff0d3de4","tid":1443752,"uid":138554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:28:32.000Z","msg":"請幫手推俾更多前線兄弟睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ca538ab0ec1e4a698c6a180dc6be087f6c286f","tid":1443752,"uid":138554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T10:49:40.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"89b299c09a053fb39005848eac91b0d626bed054","tid":1443752,"uid":138554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:15:54.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"868fce67793f6b30daed8b131d65cff9c70712fd","tid":1443752,"uid":138554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:34:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36949381f7a26ad75ad4959a75bf890316541f79","tid":1443752,"uid":138554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:32:55.000Z","msg":"又有兄弟俾狗拉 幫手推唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}